archiefmat.titel: Stukken betreffende extracten journaal Gouverneur-Generaal der Nederlandse West-Indische Bezittingen, nrs 45-124
archiefmat.titel_eng: Documents concerning some extracts from the journal of the Governor-General of the Netherlands West Indian Possessions, nos. 45-124
archiefmat.notes:
Contains muster lists of civil servants from the 1830s; the description/information in the inventory is not correct.

The data presented are based on a draft of the inventory of the archive (December 2008); numbers of the documents may change in the final version.
